msgid "Categories load dynamically..."
msgstr "分類動態載入中..."

msgid "Menu Preview"
msgstr "選單預覽"

msgid "Close"
msgstr "關閉"

msgid "Footer Preview"
msgstr "頁尾預覽"

msgid ""
"Scroll down to see your footer template. The footer below will appear on all "
"pages using this template."
msgstr "向下滾動以查看您的頁尾模板。以下頁尾將出現在使用此模板的所有頁面上。"

msgid "Close announcement"
msgstr "關閉公告"

msgid "Header Preview"
msgstr "頁首預覽"

msgid ""
"This is a preview of your header template. The header above will appear on "
"all pages using this template."
msgstr "這是您頁首模板的預覽。使用此模板的所有頁面都會顯示上方的頁首。"

msgid "Scroll down to see how the header behaves with content below it."
msgstr "向下滾動以查看頁首在下方內容中的顯示方式。"

msgid "Template Configuration"
msgstr "範本設定"

msgid "Choose and configure page templates for your storefront"
msgstr "為您的商店選擇並配置頁面模板"

msgid "Save Configuration"
msgstr "儲存設定"

msgid ""
"Choose how your checkout page looks and feels. This affects all customers."
msgstr "選擇您的結帳頁面的外觀與感覺。這會影響所有客戶。"

msgid "Options"
msgstr "選項"

msgid ""
"Configure the trust badges displayed during checkout. These appear on all "
"checkout templates when trust badges are enabled."
msgstr ""
"配置結帳時顯示的信任徽章。當啟用信任徽章時，這些徽章會出現在所有結帳模板中。"

msgid "Add Badge"
msgstr "新增徽章"

msgid "Drag to reorder. Maximum 6 badges."
msgstr "拖動以重新排序。最多 6 個徽章。"

msgid "Product Page Template"
msgstr "產品頁面範本"

msgid ""
"Choose the default product page layout. Individual products can override "
"this in their settings."
msgstr "選擇預設的產品頁面版面。單個產品可以在其設置中覆蓋此設定。"

msgid ""
"Configure trust badges for physical product pages (Classic, Full Width, "
"Gallery Focus templates)."
msgstr "為實體產品頁面（經典、全寬、畫廊重點模板）配置信任徽章。"

msgid ""
"Configure trust badges for digital product pages (software, ebooks, courses, "
"digital downloads)."
msgstr "為數位產品頁面（軟體、電子書、課程、數位下載）配置信任徽章。"

msgid "Category Page Template"
msgstr "類別頁面模板"

msgid ""
"Choose the default category page layout. Individual categories can override "
"this in their Display settings."
msgstr "選擇預設類別頁面佈局。單獨類別可以在其顯示設定中覆蓋此設定。"

msgid ""
"Choose the default blog post layout. Individual posts can override this in "
"their Design tab."
msgstr "選擇預設的部落格文章版面。個別文章可以在其設計標籤中覆蓋此設定。"

msgid "Choose the layout for the blog index page where all posts are listed."
msgstr "選擇部落格首頁的佈局，該頁面列出所有文章。"

